query:
UPDATE products 
SET categoryId = 10
WHERE name LIKE '%Aries%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Taurus%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Gemini%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Cancer%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Leo%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Virgo%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Libra%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Scorpio%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Sagittarius%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Capricorn%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Aquarius%Sun Sign%'
   OR name LIKE '%Pisces%Sun Sign%';
